---
title: Cheeseburger Meatballs with Garlicky Potato Wedges, Pickles & Special Sauce
description: Get ready for everything you love about cheeseburgers—all the flavors, all the juiciness, all the melty cheese, the taters, pickles, special sauce—without the bun! You’ll combine ground beef, cheddar, and panko to make savory, cheesy meatballs that crisp up perfectly in the oven alongside garlicky golden-brown potato wedges. While they roast, you’ll whip up a sweet and tangy special sauce of ketchup, mayonnaise, mustard, and minced pickle for the ultimate spread and dipper. Can you say: “crowd-pleaser”?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66685b27cda025ae2c6f1271-2f550c3b.jpeg
